---
import Button from "./Button.astro"
import Tag from "./Tag.astro"
---

<section class="w-full min-h-[779px] bg-slate-900" id="contact">
  <article
    class="md:rounded-tl-[100px] rounded-tl-[80px] bg-[#5c00d2] text-slate-900 align-middle
  bg-no-repeat md:bg-[url('/backgrounds/bg-contact-form-big.webp')] bg-[url('/backgrounds/bg-contact-form.webp')] bg-cover"
  >
    <article
      class="flex flex-col gap-3 content-center items-center md:max-w-[801px] max-w-80 mx-auto my-0 md:pt-32 pt-24 md:pb-32 pb-28 text-white/90"
    >
      <h2 class="md:text-5xl text-4xl leading-[52px] font-bold">Contact me</h2>
      <p
        class="text-pretty md:max-w-[569px] max-w-80 text-center text-xl leading-7 text-slate-400"
      >
        Undoubtedly, you have a fantastic idea that you'd like to transform into
        an application. I'd be delighted to assist you. Please feel free to
        contact me by leaving a message or sending an <Tag
          class="bg-indigo-900 hover:text-indigo-400"
        >
          <a href="mailto:larry_villegas@hotmail.com">emailðŸ“§</a>
        </Tag>.
      </p>
      <form
        method="POST"
        action="https://formspree.io/f/mnqyvdqr"
        class="flex flex-col gap-6 content-center items-center pt-10
        [&>label>input]:md:w-[447px] [&>label>input]:w-80 [&>label>input]:h-12 [&>label>input]:p-4 [&>label>input]:border-gray-400 [&>label>input]:text-lg [&>label>input]:leading-5 text-gray-700 [&>label>input]:rounded-lg [&>label>input]:md:rounded-none"
      >
        <label>
          <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your name" required />
        </label>
        <label>
          <input
            type="email"
            name="_replyto"
            placeholder="Your email"
            required
          />
        </label>
        <label>
          <textarea
            class="md:w-[447px] w-80 h-44 p-4 border-gray-400 text-lg leading-5 resize-none rounded-lg md:rounded-none"
            placeholder="Leave your message here"
            name="message"
            id="message"
            cols="30"
            rows="10"></textarea>
        </label>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border">
          <Button type="submit">Get in touch</Button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </article>
  </article>
</section>
